ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2009-10
PrecisAppointment of RUTH ARCHIBALD as High Commissioner for Canada to Grenada, with residence in Bridgetown; ANDRÉ BACHAND as Ambassador and Permanent Delegate of Canada to the United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization, in Paris; DAVID CHATTERSON as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Yemen, the Kingdom of Bahrain, and the Sultanate of Oman, with residence in Riyadh; MACKENZIE CLUGSTON as Ambassador of Canada to the Association of Southeast Asian Nations, with residence in Jakarta; ADÈLE DION as High Commissioner for Canada to the Kingdom of Lesotho, with residence in Pretoria; ROBERT ORR as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Zambia, with residence in Dar-es-Salaam; and VALERIE RAYMOND as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Slovak Republic, with residence in Prague.
